Description: The Company plans to build, own and operate a 25 ton per hour ("TPH") material recovery facility ("MRF") in Licking County Ohio.
Headquarters Regions: Midwestern US
Full Description: The Company plans to build, own and operate a 25 ton per hour ("TPH") material recovery facility ("MRF") in Licking County Ohio. We had a prior operation in this region that was destroyed by fire in July 2014. We formed this LLC with the intent to re-build in the region. We have excellent relationships with the regional waste haulers and will open for business with incoming material volume of over 1600 tons per month ("TPM"). We intend to grow the business to 2100 TPM in year 2 and 2600 TPM in year 3. It is our objective to provide regional waste companies and communities a viable "partner" to implement residential curbside recycling programs and community sponsored recycling programs. We differ from our competitors in that we truly look at our customers as partners and have developed a profit sharing arrangement that allows the customer to realize a profit from the collected material without having to build processing facilities. This business is scalable and we are currently looking as sites in KY and OK for our next Projects. Once operational we will also add similar products for Commercial/Industrial customers where we will work with customers to develop solutions to their current waste management programs which will focus on diverting material from landfills thereby avoiding costs for transportation and landfilling tip fees. The product offering will allow the customer to reduce costs and find value in material previously viewed as waste. We are currently seeking lease/debt financing for the Project in Licking County Ohio. We have a Venture Capital partner that has committed $600K in equity to the Project Company. In addition to the equity commitment of $600,000 we have a commitment from Westfund, LLC to provide a $300K AR line of credit once we are operational. This source of working capital is a factoring facility. Other financial structures with an investor would also be considered.

Yup, sounds like buzz word city but we actually designed a logically flawless construct for what may follow the knowledge economy out of the remnants of the industrial revolution.  It happened before, it will happen again.   Our specialty is to take whatever you have going on and run it through the filters of "The Next Economic Paradigm; An Innovation Economy Built on a Platform of Social Media" as specified by The Ingenesist Project. The result is almost certainly a very different perspective.  This perspective is useful for spotting disruption to exploit or evade in your original analysis. It's really quite an effective and flexible add-on to many consulting products.  We are often just as surprised as the client to see what emerges! Our clients include industry leaders in Aerospace, Social Media, Marketing, and Higher Education, Library Sciences, and others.   Visit our site, watch the introductory video, flip through the specification document.  Or give us a call and test our thesis.  You may be very surprised with what you hear.  Outside of consulting, we are hopeless idealists and really really think that there is an alternate financial system that can arise with a currency backed by productivity and not debt.  We believe that social capitalism is neither socialism nor capitalism - but something new which includes the biosphere as the biggest capitalist in the economy.  In spite of all the bad news, we are deeply optimistic that there is a much better way to go about traveling in circles on our little spaceship Earth.
